This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4590

A completion function that searches the current buffer.  It allows to configure the order of matches and much more.

For more see github and the accompanying blog post:
http://vertuxeltes.blogspot.de/2013/05/powerful-insert-mode-completion.html
https://github.com/dirkwallenstein/vim-localcomplete
